            . I am a <rs id="t18130407-133-viclabel705" type="occupation">scavenger</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130407-133-victim1186 t18130407-133-viclabel705"></join>. I lost the coat; on the 16th of March, out of a chaise it was standing in <placeName id="t18130407-133-crimeloc706">Dutchess-place, Portland-place</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18130407-133-crimeloc706" type="placeName" value="Dutchess-place, Portland-place"></interp>
